An Inno Setup script file that compiles the program into a Windows installer.

How to use it:

- Download the Inno Setup Compiler
- Package the program in build.py with the ONE_FILE variable set to false
- A Bit-Store.exe folder should've been created in the bin dir.
- Compile the script in Inno Setup.
- You're done! The installer will be in the created ./Output dir.
